name: I had a dream about death
description:
i had a dream about death. i was struggling in bed and at that moment i was living in two worlds: one of awake people and another where everything was just a nightmare. 
i woke up with her voice calling my name and then i understood that it was not a dream. 
i felt you die in my own flesh, as if my heart almost stopped to warn me that yours was no longer beating. 

Digital photography | 2013. 
By Silvia Maria.
